l hidden state = last encoder state&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;✦&amp;nbsp; first input token = &lt;code data-start=&quot;404&quot; data-end=&quot;410&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;GO&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; (start token embedding)&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
